<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
		<style type="text/css">
		p {
		  font-family: "Arial";
/*		  font-size: 11px;*/
		}

		h1 {
		  font-family: "Arial";
/*		  font-size: 14px;*/
		}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<p>Welcome <%= @email %>!</p>

		<h1><p> You have made the excellent choice of registering as a host at Meet the Danes.</p></h1>

		<p> This is an outstanding opportunity to meet people from around the world. </p>

		<p> As a host you are expected to serve 3 courses – it might be Danish or Continental cuisine it's up to you. With the food you can serve wine or beer depending on the dish. </p>

		<p> As a host you will receive a payment of <%= @commision %>% of the total guest payment. The amount will be on your account 3 days before the event.</p>

		<p>Please remember it’s optional – meaning it’s up to you if you want to reject or accept an invitation from a guest. We just want you to have a great experience.
		Once you've confirmed your account, you'll be ask to fill out your personal profile and create an experience (event). Please do this as thoroughly as possible.</p>

		<p><strong>Your profile and your experience will be featured on the site as soon as you have been approved by Meet the Danes. You will be notified of approval via email.</strong></p>

		<p>You can confirm your account email through the link below:</p>

		<p><%= link_to 'Confirm my account', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %></p>
	</body>
</html>



 
 

 

 




